      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a mint-condition example that presents exceptionally well throughout. The paint, interior, and overall finish show minimal wear, and the car has clearly been very well cared for over time. This is not just a decent driver\u2014it is the kind of vehicle that stands out for its cleanliness, strong presentation, and well-preserved condition. Buyers should expect a highly attractive, thoroughly cared-for example that is ready to enjoy and likely to appeal to anyone looking for one of the better cars on the market.",
