    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer seeking affordable transportation or a practical project. It shows wear consistent with its age and use, but presents as an opportunity to get into a car at a very accessible price point. A sensible choice for someone who prioritizes low upfront cost and real-world utility.",
