    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life and a bit of project potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a handy fixer-upper. It has honest wear consistent with age and use, and it\u2019s priced to make a lot of sense for the right buyer. If you want something inexpensive, practical, and worth a look, this could be a great fit.",
