      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014the sort of machine that feels like it has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an ideal canvas for someone who appreciates grit, personality, and the satisfaction of bringing out a vehicle\u2019s next chapter. Whether you need an affordable runabout, a project with soul, or a practical set of wheels with unmistakable presence, this one offers a rare chance to get in at a budget-friendly price and make it your own.",
